OL,3,CLionesses star Missy Bo Kearns reveals
OL,4,Cshe lost baby during pregnancy
OL,6,FAston Villa midfielder Missy Bo Kearns
OL,7,Fhas revealed that she and her partner,
OL,8,FLuton midfielder Liam Walsh, have lost
OL,9,Ftheir child during pregnancy.
OL,11,FThe couple announced they were
OL,12,Fexpecting in a video posted to social
OL,13,Fmedia earlier this month showing the
OL,14,Fpair painting "mum + dad" onto a wall
OL,15,Falong with the September due date, and
OL,16,Fproudly holding ultrasound scans.
OL,18,FEngland international Kearns, 24, took
OL,19,Fto Instagram on Sunday night to share
OL,20,Fthe sad news in a post to her Stories.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@YO]
