OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774937073
OL,3,CLionesses star Missy Bo Kearns reveals
OL,4,Cshe lost baby during pregnancy
OL,6,FShe wrote: "With very heavy hearts, we
OL,7,Fwant to share that we've lost our baby
OL,8,Fduring pregnancy.
OL,10,F"The past weeks have been filled with
OL,11,Fa kind of sadness that's hard to
OL,12,Fexplain, and we're still trying to
OL,13,Fcome to terms with it all.
OL,15,F"Right now, we're focusing on
OL,16,Frecovering and supporting each other
OL,17,Fthrough this. We truly appreciate the
OL,18,Flove and support around us more than
OL,19,Fwe can say."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
