OL,3,CLionesses star Missy Bo Kearns reveals
OL,4,Cshe lost baby during pregnancy
OL,6,FWalsh, 28, shared the same post to his
OL,7,FStories.
OL,9,FAston Villa Women offered their
OL,10,Fcondolences on X, in a post reading:
OL,11,F"We are sending all our love and
OL,12,Fsupport to Missy Bo and Liam at this
OL,13,Fdifficult time."
OL,15,FLuton wrote on X: "We send all our
OL,16,Flove and support to Liam, Missy Bo,
OL,17,Fand their families at this deeply sad
OL,18,Ftime."
